title: Phish - Big Cypress Seminole Indian Reservation, FL (1999) [V0]
description:
Live Recordings of the Concert:
Includes Dec: 29th, 30th, & 31st (Total 93 tracks)

All files downloaded from phish.in and organized into folder structures after. Track #'s & Album Names have been edited to portray each Day as a separate Album group, and each set as a separate Album. Source is unknown, but bit rate is V0. Sound is good for a Live recording

*some track have had descriptors added in parentheses to track titles to avoid duplicate names on the same CD.
